{"data":[{"date":"16:31 25/06","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u, \u201cch\u00fa d\u00ea\u201d Messi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed3n?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/goc-nhin-chung-kien-ronaldo-thi-dau-chu-de-messi-co-buon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u00e0 c\u1eb7p k\u1ef3 ph\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong 10 n\u0103m qua, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa 2 si\u00eau nh\u00e2n n\u00e0y \u0111ang c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ronaldo v\u1eabn t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, c\u00e1c C\u0110V l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nT\u1eeb &ldquo;ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u d\u00ea&rdquo; c\u1ee7a CR7<br>\r\n<em>&nbsp;</em></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>&ldquo;Quaresma n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nu\u00f4i ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u n\u1ebfu ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ng\u00e0y mai&rdquo;</em> &ndash; <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ly-do-hai-huoc-khien-ronaldo-quyet-dinh-nuoi-rau-de-421-189143.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00e2u</span>, 1 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1edf World Cup. \u0110\u00f3 v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a CR7, khi anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 lu\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111i\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e0, ch\u1ea3i chu\u1ed1t, Ronaldo l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 g\u00e3 &ldquo;th\u1ea7y tu&rdquo; \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a \u1edf cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng. Khi c\u00f2n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o M.U, m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00e0 Ronaldo &ndash; h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Evra l\u1ea1i ph\u00e1t ho\u1ea3ng khi th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e0n em ch\u1ec9 u\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ecdc v\u00e0 \u0103n th\u1ecbt tr\u1eafng, tuy\u1ec7t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n c\u1ee7a CR7. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u00ecnh x\u0103m n\u00e0o. Th\u1eadm cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33 &ndash; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong \u0111\u1eddi Ronaldo&hellip; nu\u00f4i r\u00e2u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fa d\u00ea Messi c\u00f3 bu\u1ed3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Goc-nhin-Chung-kien-Ronaldo-thi-dau,-chu-de-Messi-co-buon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo v\u00e0 &quot;ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u d\u00ea&quot; m\u1edbi nu\u00f4i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ec9nh cao trong su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m li\u1ec1n, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u1eabn nh\u01b0 ch\u00e0ng trai 23 tu\u1ed5i, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i kh\u1ed5 luy\u1ec7n h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh. Sau tu\u1ed5i 30, Ronaldo ti\u1ebfn h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm, \u01b0a th\u00edch v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng cho d\u00f9 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t anh ch\u00e0ng m\u00e0u m\u00e8, \u01b0a bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n t\u1ea1i \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0o Euro 2004, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Ronaldo thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 g\u00e1nh c\u1ea3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u00ean vai. Anh \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 b\u1eaft c\u1ea3 \u0110T ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i B\u0110N nh\u01b0 bao ki\u1ebfm, t\u1ea1o m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 thanh g\u01b0\u01a1m Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t v\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/iran-vs-bo-dao-nha-01h00-ngay-266-kho-can-cr7-421-189482.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0110T Iran</span>. T\u1ea1i sao n\u00f3i &ldquo;g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i&rdquo;, b\u1edfi v\u00ec b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ea1i World Cup, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi Iran (n\u0103m 2006 t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c). V\u00e0 trong k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u1edfi \u00edt ra, Ronaldo c\u0169ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup: Ronaldo 4 - Messi 0\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Ronaldo 4 - Messi 0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h2>V\u00e0 &ldquo;ch\u00fa d\u00ea&rdquo; t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p Lionel Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 mang ti\u1ebfng &ldquo;c\u00f4ng t\u1eed&rdquo;, &ldquo;con nh\u00e0 l\u00e0nh&rdquo;, Messi c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng k\u00e9m ai \u1edf kho\u1ea3n x\u0103m h\u00ecnh hay&hellip; nu\u00f4i r\u00e2u, nhu\u1ed9m t\u00f3c. Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m di\u1ec5n ra VCK World Cup, anh c\u00f2n cho ra l\u00f2 b\u1ed9 \u1ea3nh ch\u1ee5p c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t con d\u00ea (goat), v\u1edbi \u00fd ngh\u0129a<strong> &ldquo;Greastest of All Time&rdquo; </strong>(hay nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i). T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Messi qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, n\u00ean anh c\u00f3 t\u1ef1 tin m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng sao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/cuu-sao-barca-che-messi-khong-bang-ronaldo-421-189430.html\" target=\"_blank\">Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Ronaldo</span> &ndash; \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia. Messi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f9ng Argentina, khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. V\u00e0 c\u1ee9 sau m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, anh l\u1ea1i thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta&hellip; th\u1ea5t t\u00ecnh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/mess.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, Messi l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1eabu th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh g\u1ed3ng g\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, hay th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn Argentina ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. Jorge Sampaoli, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Argentina hi\u1ec7n nay, n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh theo&hellip; s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a El Pulga.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Icardi v\u00e0 Dybala r\u1ea5t hay, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf nh\u00e0, ng\u01b0\u1eddi &ldquo;m\u00f2n \u0111\u00edt&rdquo; d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00ec Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch. Higuain, d\u00f9 lu\u00f4n v\u00f4 duy\u00ean trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn, v\u1eabn g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n, ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec Messi th\u00edch. Hay nh\u01b0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-bao-ve-messi-sau-tran-thua-tham-cua-argentina-465-189202.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sampaoli th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch&hellip; to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Argentina</span>, v\u00ec &ldquo;d\u00e1m&rdquo; che m\u1edd v\u1ea7ng h\u00e0o quang c\u1ee7a Messi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hay n\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c, Albiceleste kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 10. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Messi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 &ldquo;g\u00e1nh&rdquo; \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia theo \u00fd, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo \u0111ang l\u00e0m. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh CR7 l\u00e0 &ldquo;thanh ki\u1ebfm&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n quanh &ldquo;v\u1ecf bao&rdquo; B\u0110N, Messi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc khi\u00ean \u0111\u1ee1 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Argentina &ndash; \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t b\u1edfi Croatia 3 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n cho&hellip; Nigeria h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Iceland \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2. V\u00e0 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00e0n lan b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh Messi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Nigeria, 2 tay gi\u01a1 cao v\u00e0 \u0103n m\u1eebng nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 ch\u00f2m r\u00e2u c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Messi h\u1eb3n r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Nigeria th\u1eafng Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/messsi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi h\u1eb3n r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Nigeria th\u1eafng Iceland</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Leo \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n. Trong bu\u1ed5i sinh nh\u1eadt m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y (24/6) c\u1ee7a anh, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u vui v\u1ebb v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi b\u1ecf n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n thua tr\u1eadn sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean. Messi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t keo h\u00e0n g\u1eafn v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2y ra b\u1edfi Sampaoli.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thua-tham-croatia-argentina-phai-lam-gi-de-vuot-qua-vong-bang-421-189208.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Argentina bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Nigeria</span>. V\u00e0 th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn, khi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng m\u1ed3i quen thu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i World Cup n\u00e0o Nigeria kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p Argentina, th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3&hellip; kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i World Cup. Trong 6 l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u Phi 5 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p Albiceleste, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 thua 4 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ed1 10 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. B\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng, n\u1ebfu Messi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 &ldquo;ch\u00fa d\u00ea&rdquo; t\u1ef1 phong, v\u00e0 cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u00ecn Ronaldo &ldquo;v\u1ec3nh r\u00e2u&rdquo; h\u1ebft tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y sang tr\u1eadn kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si-389-189418.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si-389-189418.html\">Tu\u1ed5i 31 c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi: M\u1ed9t \u0111am m\u00ea, m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1i kh\u1edd, m\u1ed9t Si</span><br>\r\n4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Messi \u0111\u00f3n sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 27 b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ng\u1eadp tr\u00e0n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac trong tr\u1eadn Argentina th\u1eafng Nigeria 3-2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. 4 n\u0103m sau &ndash;...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ha-nhuc-argentina-sao-croatia-con-khinh-bi-khong-them-doi-ao-voi-messi-421-189368.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/ha-nhuc-argentina-sao-croatia-con-khinh-bi-khong-them-doi-ao-voi-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ha-nhuc-argentina-sao-croatia-con-khinh-bi-khong-them-doi-ao-voi-messi-421-189368.html\">H\u1ea1 nh\u1ee5c Argentina, sao Croatia c\u00f2n &ldquo;khinh b\u1ec9&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m \u0111\u1ed5i \u00e1o v\u1edbi Messi</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Argentina &ndash; Rebic coi th\u01b0\u1eddng Messi v\u00e0 qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/20180621T195318Z_273911651_RC1220A4E800_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPARGCRO.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-argentina-vs-croatia-461-189198.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Argentina 0-3 Croatia (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1eafng Argentina 3-0 h\u00f4m 21/6, Croatia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi khi\u1ebfn Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi hi\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"569","checkdouble":"189520"},{"date":"16:35 25/06","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/u19-viet-nam-ton-that-nhan-su-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn ca ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.</h2><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e3y tay tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh  tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh  tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/tien-anh-0007.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh B c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u01b0\u01a1ng Ti\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may b\u1ecb g\u00e3y tay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande B, Ti\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e3 \u1edf t\u01b0 th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng tay ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111au. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ee5p phim cho th\u1ea5y Ti\u1ebfn Anh b\u1ecb g\u00e3y x\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e1nh tay v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Ti\u1ebfn Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, khi m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (25/6) th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ri\u00eang Ti\u1ebfn Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1n b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a VFF \u1edf l\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u00eam \u00edt ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o VFF sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb, \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Ti\u1ebfn Anh c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadp trung \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. V\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eeba g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i, Ti\u1ebfn Anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"568","checkdouble":"189523"},{"date":"16:42 25/06","title":"\"Th\u00e1nh h\u1ed5\" d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ra sao v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/thanh-ho-du-doan-ra-sao-ve-ket-qua-tran-uruguay-vs-nga.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 John Stones ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Everton trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh vs B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh hai v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/quy-tac-xep-hang-bang-dau-world-cup-2018-tai-sao-anh-vs-bi-co-the-phan-dinh-nhat-nhi-bang-the-phat-421-189499.html\">Quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh vs B\u1ec9 Stones th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Lukaku ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anh vs B\u1ec9 Stones th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Lukaku ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stones h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Lukaku \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 John Stones, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Harry Kane khi ghi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Anh 6-1 Panama, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Romelu Lukaku, ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn \u0111ang th\u0103ng hoa phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi 4 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Stones v\u00e0 Lukaku t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nhau trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Everton tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn hai n\u1eeda th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i cho m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i v\u00e0 Rom t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Everton. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1eady n\u00ean Man Utd m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ch\u1ecbu chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh \u1ea5y. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng mong ng\u00f3ng m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi Rom.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189373.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia</span> v\u00e0 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n ngh\u00eanh chi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u00ec qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e2 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-tunisia-lukaku-nguoi-di-tim-cau-tra-loi-cho-moi-cau-hoi-421-189389.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/san-bang-thanh-tich-cua-ronaldo-lukaku-noi-gi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-tunisia-lukaku-nguoi-di-tim-cau-tra-loi-cho-moi-cau-hoi-421-189389.html\">B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia: Lukaku \u2013 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i t\u00ecm c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho m\u1ecdi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi</span><br>\r\n\u1ede s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 World Cup, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mang danh \u201cch\u00e2n g\u1ed7\u201d hay \u201ckh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o\u201d nh\u01b0 Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e0n anh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"567","checkdouble":"189524"},{"date":"17:18 25/06","title":"Carragher: \"\u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n b\u00f3p n\u00e1t B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jamie Carragher, \u0110T Anh n\u00ean b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i.</h2><h2>Anh v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 tranh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m qua sau khi \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i Panama v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 6-1 t\u1ea1i Nizhny Novgorod. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick, qua \u0111\u00f3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng G, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi-421-189527.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 Carragher cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Tam S\u01b0 g\u1eedi chi\u1ebfn th\u01b0 t\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Carragher hy v\u1ecdng Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Carragher hy v\u1ecdng Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/carragher-dt-can-bop-nat-bi-o-tran-dau-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Carragher hy v\u1ecdng Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n cho Anh, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Brazil ho\u1eb7c \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Senegal c\u00f3 Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Ismaila Sarr trong khi Colombia c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u1eafc c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng l\u1ea1c quan m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Iceland c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 thay v\u00ec ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out. Gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra ni\u1ec1m tin trong l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edch nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0110T Anh\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Anh kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf th\u1ebf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Carragher, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cKh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u1edf Champions League, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng cao h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ea1c quan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ti\u1ebfp theo m\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Southgate c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi-421-189527.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 Lukaku trong tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/courtois-len-day-cot-tinh-than-truoc-dai-chien-voi-dt-anh-421-189486.html\">Courtois l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"566","checkdouble":"189525"},{"date":"16:53 25/06","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0103n may, kh\u00f3 \u0111i s\u00e2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/hlv-le-thuy-hai-nhan-dinh-dt-nhat-ban-an-may-kho-di-sau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng may v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ph\u00f9 tang kh\u00f3 \u0111i s\u00e2u.</h2><h2>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng may</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, \u2018c\u00e1c Samurai xanh\u2019 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Senegal ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Le Thuy Hai tu tin co the lam tot vi tri GDKT o doi tuyen Viet Nam\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed G\u0110KT \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/10/22/hlv-hai-lo-toi-tu-tin-co-the-lam-tot-gdkt-o-doi-tuyen.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i xa t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 tr\u00ean Vietnamnet: \u201cTh\u1ef1c ra b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec gh\u00ea g\u1edbm c\u1ea3.\u00a0\u1ede\u00a0tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Colombia m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1edbm v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i trong hi\u1ec7p 2 n\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.Tr\u1eadn h\u00f4m qua Nh\u1eadt c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n g\u00ec\u00a0Senegal, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed may m\u1eafn g\u1ee1\u00a0h\u00f2a v\u00e0 c\u1ed1\u00a0gi\u1eef\u00a0k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3\u00a0\u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam: \u201c\u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd\u00a0Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nhanh, nh\u1ecf, ban b\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi th\u1ec3\u00a0h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 th\u1ec3\u00a0l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hai tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua h\u1ecd\u00a0kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3\u00a0hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. T\u00f4i xin nh\u1eafc l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong th\u00ec c\u0169ng l\u00e0 do may m\u1eafn b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7\u00a0t\u1ef1\u00a0thua, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp th\u00ec c\u0169ng th\u1ebf\u00a0th\u00f4i, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa \u0111\u00e2u\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u G\u0110KT Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cB\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec v\u1ee9t, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 World Cup. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9\u00a0khen Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3\u00a0c\u1ea3m, chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1t th\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c ra \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o t\u1edbi World Cup ch\u1eb3ng v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0\u00a0Panama h\u1ecd\u00a0thua \u0111\u1eadm nh\u01b0\u00a0th\u1ebf\u00a0nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0c\u00f3 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1. Ba Lan c\u0169ng v\u1eady, h\u1ecd\u00a0b\u1ecb\u00a0lo\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd\u00a0bu\u00f4ng xu\u00f4i c\u1ea3. H\u00e3y c\u1ee9\u00a0xem tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0\u00a0n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\u201d, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n l\u00e3o l\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam hy v\u1ecdng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp song \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Akira Nishino b\u1edfi t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup</span> c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 chung kh\u00e1t khao chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo-421-189462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuc-dien-bang-h-truoc-luot-tran-cuoi-cho-doi-nhung-bat-ngo-421-189462.html\">C\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n b\u1ea3ng H tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i: \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Colombia gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. V\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-nhat-ban-sang-cua-di-tiep-dung-coi-thuong-nhung-chang-lun-466-189471.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/dt-nhat-ban-sang-cua-di-tiep-dung-coi-thuong-nhung-chang-lun.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/dt-nhat-ban-sang-cua-di-tiep-dung-coi-thuong-nhung-chang-lun-466-189471.html\">\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: \u0110\u1eebng coi th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng l\u00f9n</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi HLV Akira Nishino ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u1edbi con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hoa-qua-cam-cua-dt-nhat-ban-truoc-senegal-421-189460.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/Du-am-Nhat-Ban-2-2-Senegal-Tinh-than-Samurai-va-niem-hy-vong-chau-A-hinh-anh-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-hoa-qua-cam-cua-dt-nhat-ban-truoc-senegal-421-189460.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 hai l\u1ea7n san h\u00f2a c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"565","checkdouble":"189526"},{"date":"17:16 25/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 Lukaku trong tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 John Stones ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Everton trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh vs B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh hai v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/quy-tac-xep-hang-bang-dau-world-cup-2018-tai-sao-anh-vs-bi-co-the-phan-dinh-nhat-nhi-bang-the-phat-421-189499.html\">Quy t\u1eafc x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i trong b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh vs B\u1ec9 Stones th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Lukaku ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anh vs B\u1ec9 Stones th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Lukaku ng\u00e0y t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stones h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Lukaku \u1edf \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Anh vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec trung v\u1ec7 John Stones, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Harry Kane khi ghi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Anh 6-1 Panama, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Romelu Lukaku, ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn \u0111ang th\u0103ng hoa phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi 4 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Stones v\u00e0 Lukaku t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean nhau trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Everton tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn hai n\u1eeda th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i cho m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i v\u00e0 Rom t\u1eebng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai ng\u00e0y c\u00f2n c\u00f9ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Everton. Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1eady n\u00ean Man Utd m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ch\u1ecbu chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh \u1ea5y. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng mong ng\u00f3ng m\u00e0n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi Rom.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-con-mua-ban-thang-tran-bi-vs-tunisia-421-189373.html\" target=\"_blank\">B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia</span> v\u00e0 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n ngh\u00eanh chi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u00ec qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e2 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Roberto Martinez.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-tunisia-lukaku-nguoi-di-tim-cau-tra-loi-cho-moi-cau-hoi-421-189389.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/san-bang-thanh-tich-cua-ronaldo-lukaku-noi-gi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-tunisia-lukaku-nguoi-di-tim-cau-tra-loi-cho-moi-cau-hoi-421-189389.html\">B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia: Lukaku \u2013 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i t\u00ecm c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho m\u1ecdi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi</span><br>\r\n\u1ede s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i danh gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 World Cup, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mang danh \u201cch\u00e2n g\u1ed7\u201d hay \u201ckh\u00f4ng n\u00e3o\u201d nh\u01b0 Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e0n anh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"564","checkdouble":"189527"},{"date":"17:23 25/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp 21h00 ng\u00e0y 25/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/truc-tiep-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ai C\u1eadp vs Saudi Arabia b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 25/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft q