0y h\u00f4m nay 25/6.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-uruguay-vs-nga-463-189532.html\" target=\"_blank\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP URUGUAY VS NGA</strong></u></span><u><strong><br>\r\n</strong></u></span><br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"562","checkdouble":"189532"},{"date":"17:58 25/06","title":"Juventus chi 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro s\u0103n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Atletico","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/juventus-mua-godin-gia-20-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid song \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Godin</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDiego Godin gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid n\u0103m 2010 t\u1eeb Villarreal. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay d\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua. C\u00f9ng nhau, h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh 7 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2 n\u0103m 2014 v\u00e0 2016.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGodin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 hi\u1ebfm hoi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Ngo\u00e0i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng, \u1edf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n to\u00e1t ra phong th\u00e1i th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh. Th\u00eam n\u1eefa, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Trong 8 m\u00f9a \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i cho Atletico, trung b\u00ecnh m\u1ed7i m\u00f9a Godin c\u00f3 g\u1ea7n 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. C\u00e1 bi\u1ec7t c\u00f3 m\u00f9a 2013/14, anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 8 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/juventus-mua-godin-gia-20-trieu-euro.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Godin ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Godin \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32. V\u00e0 d\u00f9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Uruguay ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, ph\u00eda Atletico c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng Jose Gimenez, Stefan Savic, Lucas Hernandez tr\u1ebb trung h\u01a1n v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Godin.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Atletico</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin tr\u00ean, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, trung v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 Atletico mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u00e0i h\u01a1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Godin phat bieu ve Salah\" title=\"Godin ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/diego-godin-ai-cap-co-salah-hay-khong-cung-vay-thoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Godin gi\u00e1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Juventus th\u00ec kh\u00e1c. Sau khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Leonardo Bonucci ra \u0111i, \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi 3 trung v\u1ec7. T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Beppe Marotta hi\u1ec7n mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh m\u1edbi cho h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Godin, \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf m\u1ecdi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng x\u1ea3y ra. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1edbt l\u1edd. C\u00f2n Atletico, \u0111\u1ec3 Godin ra \u0111i v\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 20 tri\u1ec7u Euro ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng anh sau \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/juventus-ra-gia-pjanic-it-nhat-80-trieu-euro-176-189062.html\">Juventus b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t cho Real v\u00e0 Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nhan-don-dau-vu-sao-juventus-172-188630.html\">Chelsea nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus-176-188909.html\">CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-tu-choi-mua-sao-khung-juventus-voi-gia-53-trieu-bang-172-188375.html\">MU t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"561","checkdouble":"189533"},{"date":"17:55 25/06","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/25/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-ba-lan-03-colombia.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ba Lan vs Colombia b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Yerry Mina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1, Yerry Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Davinson Sanchez. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham kh\u00f3a ch\u1eb7t trung phong Robert Lewandowski c\u1ee7a Ba Lan.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ba Lan vs Colombia b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Ba Lan vs Colombia b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Diem-nhan-Ba-Lan-vs-Colombia-bang-H-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Anh c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 4 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3i nguy k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 40, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a James Rodriguez, Mina ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Wojciech Szczesny \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n qua \u0111\u00f3 mang v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Colombia. Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 b\u00e0n cho \u0110TQG, 3 b\u00e0n trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1edfi Ba Lan bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Colombia ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Barca h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n anh v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca trao th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Robert Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Robert Lewandowski l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ba Lan \u1edf World Cup 2018, song nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn thua Senegal anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayern tung ra 3 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mot minh Robert Lewandowski khong the giup Ba Lan gianh nhung chien thang\" title=\"M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Robert Lewandowski kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ba Lan gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-DT-Ba-Lan-tham-bai-truoc-Colombia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Lewandowski ch\u01b0a khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng H v\u1edbi Colombia, Lewandowski ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 tung ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Lewandowski \u1edf World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Ba Lan ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 2 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i anh c\u00f3 8 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, 3 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLewandowski \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng n\u01a1i NHM, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i b\u1edfi anh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng, vi\u1ec7c anh ch\u01a1i c\u00e1ch xa khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u1ea3m \u0111i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: James Rodriguez</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 1-2, James Rodriguez khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Colombia kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"James Rodriguez co 2 kien tao truoc Ba Lan\" title=\"James Rodriguez c\u00f3 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Thong-ke-Ba-Lan-vs-Colombia---Bang-H-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>James Rodriguez c\u00f3 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-ba-lan-vs-colombia-463-189436.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ba Lan vs Colombia</span> b\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Mina m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 anh tung \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Cuadrado \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u1ea7n l\u1edbn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Colombia \u0111\u1ec1u qua ch\u00e2n James Rodriguez, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 2/3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng World Cup, James Rodriguez \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Colombia, bao g\u1ed3m 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 4 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, James Rodriguez ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Colombia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Senegal \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng H, qua \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Abel Aguilar</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan, Abel Aguilar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u1edbi Wilmar Barrios. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong kho\u1ea3ng 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn, anh gi\u00fap Colombia ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Abel Aguilar dinh chan thuong dui kha nghiem trong\" title=\"Abel Aguilar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Abel Aguilar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 31, Abel Aguilar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng sau m\u1ed9t pha va ch\u1ea1m. D\u00f9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean y t\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Mateus Uribe.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n, Abel Aguilar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i. V\u1edbi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Senegal, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Radamel Falcao</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd: \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 32 nh\u01b0ng Radamel Falcao v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n n\u00e0o cho Colombia \u1edf World Cup.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Falcao ghi ban nhan doi cach biet cho DT Colombia.\" title=\"Falcao ghi b\u00e0n nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t cho \u0110T Colombia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Falcao c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Colombia d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Brazil. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1986 r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u <br>\r\ntr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Falcao c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Ba Lan.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Juan Quinteroa, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u1ea9y m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Wojciech Szczesny bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec Falcao c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Ba Lan gi\u00fap Colombia th\u1eafp l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Senegal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, Senegal b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Senegal tu dat minh vao the kho khi de Nhat Ban cam hoa 2-2\" title=\"Senegal t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi \u0111\u1ec3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/senegal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Senegal t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi \u0111\u1ec3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 2-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSenegal \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Mane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-2. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Senegal t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-dt-ba-lan-tham-bai-truoc-colombia-421-189472.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-dt-ba-lan-tham-bai-truoc-colombia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-dt-ba-lan-tham-bai-truoc-colombia-421-189472.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ba Lan th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia?</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Kazan Arena t\u1ed1i 24/6, \u0110T Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia trong th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, song \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i Senegal ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 thua Colombia.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n* Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"560","checkdouble":"189535"},{"date":"09:21 25/06","title":"\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Barca vs Real v\u00ec sao tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-va-real-muon-mua-thiago-alcantara.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara, hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Bayern Munich. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n y\u00eau c\u1ea7u n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ra \u0111i l\u00ean t\u1edbi 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Thiago</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nThiago Alcantara t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Barcelona trong v\u00f2ng 6 n\u0103m (2005 t\u1edbi 2011). D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f4n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i 1 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou mu\u1ed1n anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebf t\u1ee5c cho c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n Xavi v\u00e0 Andres Iniesta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Thiago kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi ng\u00e0y \u1ea5y. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi hai bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00f3i tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barca, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ra \u0111i. \u0110\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2013/14, Thiago \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Guardiola t\u1ea1i Bayern Munich.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara, hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i cho Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara, hi\u1ec7n ch\u01a1i cho Bayern h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/barca-va-real-muon-mua-thiago-alcantara.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Thiago Alcantara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng m\u00f9a 2014/15, qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Thiago h\u1ed3i sinh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c. Qua \u0111\u00f3, anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i gia bao g\u1ed3m ch\u00ednh CLB th\u1eddi ni\u00ean thi\u1ebfu Barcelona. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia m\u1edbi chia tay Iniesta (sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n) v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Andre Gomes hay Denis Suarez kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi HLV Ernesto Valverde.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>El Clasico v\u00ec tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Sport \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Barca d\u00f9 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Thiago nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Real c\u00f3 v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u00e0 HLV Julen Lopetegui trong tay. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos thay Zinedine Zidane n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay sau m\u00f9a 2017/18.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara dinh chan thuong nghiem trong\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Guardiola, Lopetegui l\u00e0 HLV c\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Thiago. H\u1ecd c\u00f9ng nhau g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i U19 t\u1edbi U21 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t n\u0103m 2012 v\u00e0 2013. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Thiago, Real coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Bayern Munich s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 Thiago ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro. M\u1ed9t con s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ch\u1edd xem Real v\u00e0 Barca ai s\u1ebd b\u1ea1o tay h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea-172-189414.html\">Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sao-man-city-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-barca-180-189345.html\">Sao Man City c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nham-sao-barca-nang-cap-hang-thu-172-189276.html\">MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-mua-sao-mu-sau-su-ra-di-cua-iniesta-180-189268.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n mua sao M.U sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"559","checkdouble":"189489"},{"date":"09:46 25/06","title":"M.U c\u1eed \u0111i\u1ec7p vi\u00ean th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i sao s\u00e1ng Serbia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/mu-muon-mua-milinkovicsavic-va-dung-chieu-doc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang b\u1eadn chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Nga c\u00f9ng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, nh\u01b0ng Hazard chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nConte \u0111i, Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 gi\u00fap The Blues gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap FA g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng HLV Antonio Conte v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u1ecb ng\u1eebng l\u1ea1i do nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i Conte, khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf ra to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Juventus c\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 khi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i n\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, khi The Blues s\u1ebd c\u00f3 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi trong v\u00f2ng 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi &ndash; theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh. HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea sau nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u1ecb Napoli sa th\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 do l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf\" title=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Daily Star c\u00f2n cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam, HLV Sarri y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf khu Cobham, Surrey, g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a CLB. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, c\u00f9ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. 2 b\u00ean s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Sarri c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1eddi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea &ndash; Gianfranco Zola gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, v\u00ec The Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Hazard hay Courtois c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 t\u00e2n HLV v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed cho bi\u1ebft s\u1edf d\u0129 Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111u\u1ed5i Diego Costa qua tin nh\u1eafn, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh b\u1ecb s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m th\u00ea th\u1ea3m (b\u00e1n cho Atletico v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"558","checkdouble":"189490"},{"date":"09:05 25/06","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp (21h00 ng\u00e0y 25/6): \u0110i t\u00ecm chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/nhan-dinh-saudi-arabia-vs-ai-cap-21h00-ngay-256-di-tim-chien-thang-lich-su.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ea3 Saudi Arabia l\u1eabn Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</h2><h2>C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 Saudi Arabia l\u1eabn Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i sau khi lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai k\u1ebft th\u00fac. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m nay ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh xem \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSaudi Arabia hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Uruguay \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai. V\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Saeed Al-Owairan h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c B\u1ec9 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m 1994.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp (21h00 ng\u00e0y 256) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp (21h00 ng\u00e0y 256) h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Saudi-Arabia-vs-Ai-Cap.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAi C\u1eadp th\u00ec th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. \u1ede l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1990, Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng si\u00eau sao Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc Phi. Salah v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> g\u1eb7p Uruguay v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng anh ch\u01b0a b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.</div>\r\n<h2>Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Ai C\u1eadp l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Hector Cuper c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ngo\u00e0i s\u1ef1 \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Mohamed Salah, Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trui r\u00e8n \u1edf Anh nh\u01b0 Elmohamady, Elneny hay Sobhi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah khong the giup Ai Cap danh bai Nga\" title=\"Salah kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Salah kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Saudi Arabia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, c\u1ea3 23 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n T\u00e2y \u00c1 \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc. Vi\u1ec7c qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Al-Sahlawi c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i, trong khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu 6 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c si\u00eau sao Mohamed Salah \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Salah \u0111ang l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n s\u1ed1ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Pharaoh&rdquo; khi ghi t\u1edbi 5/7 b\u00e0n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. M\u1ed9t khi Salah l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap Ai C\u1eadp ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Salah v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp:</strong><br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf Confederations Cup n\u0103m 1999. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 5-1.<br>\r\n- Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho Saudi Arabia ho\u1eb7c Ai C\u1eadp \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thua c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Honduras n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n- Saudi Arabia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 11 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup. Honduras v\u00e0 Algeria n\u0103m 2010 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n- Saudi Arabia gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng trong 12 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n- \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ai C\u1eadp \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf World Cup.<br>\r\n- 8 b\u00e0n thua g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ai C\u1eadp t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Saudi Arabia vs Ai Cap\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/Saudi-Arabia-vs-Ai-Cap-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-2-3-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1: 1-2</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Saudi Arabia vs Ai C\u1eadp:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/salah-len-tieng-sau-khi-ai-cap-som-bi-loai-khoi-world-cup-421-189235.html\">Salah l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi Ai C\u1eadp s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/phu-thuoc-lionel-messi-argentina-co-hon-gi-ai-cap-466-189215.html\">Ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c Lionel Messi, Argentina c\u00f3 h\u01a1n g\u00ec... Ai C\u1eadp?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"557","checkdouble":"189491"},{"date":"10:29 25/06","title":"Kanu: \"Nigeria s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-brasil-vs-costa-rica.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Nwankwo Kanu tin r\u1eb1ng Nigeria c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><h2>Nigeria c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Gernot Rohr \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafp b\u1eebng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng thua trong tr\u1eadn t\u1eed chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Argentina t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Krestovsky ng\u00e0y mai, Nigeria s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/argentina-that-bai-khi-sampaoli-lac-me-hon-tran-421-189252.html\" target=\"_blank\">Argentina \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</span>. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, La Albiceleste c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kanu Nigeria s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kanu Nigeria s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-brasil-vs-costa-rica.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kanu tin Nigeria s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Nwankwo Kanu tin r\u1eb1ng Nigeria th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ea1y cho Argentina m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNigeria vs Argentina. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 tin kh\u00f4ng? Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng? T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d, Kanu chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u k\u00e9m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Rohr \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i Krasnodar. Nh\u01b0ng trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, Argentina v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Nigeria.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1eafng La Albiceleste trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed FIFA World Cup. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArgentina \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm sau hai tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng Nigeria, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Iceland th\u1eafng Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Argentina s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Iceland tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu Iceland kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Croatia, Argentina ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-chi-chia-tay-dt-argentina-voi-mot-dieu-kien-421-189475.html\">Messi ch\u1ec9 chia tay \u0110T Argentina v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/noi-bo-tuyen-argentina-dang-roi-nhu-canh-he-421-189422.html\">N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 canh h\u1eb9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"556","checkdouble":"189492"},{"date":"10:47 25/06","title":"Hazard chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/hazard-chuan-bi-co-thay-moi-trong-24-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110ang b\u1eadn chinh chi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Nga c\u00f9ng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia, nh\u01b0ng Hazard chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y m\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nConte \u0111i, Sarri \u0111\u1ebfn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 gi\u00fap The Blues gi\u00e0nh 2 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap FA g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng HLV Antonio Conte v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Abramovich \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia t\u1eeb giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u1ecb ng\u1eebng l\u1ea1i do nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 visa, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i Conte, khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf ra to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Juventus c\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ed9 khi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i n\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, khi The Blues s\u1ebd c\u00f3 thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi trong v\u00f2ng 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi &ndash; theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh. HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea sau nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng c\u0169ng m\u1edbi b\u1ecb Napoli sa th\u1ea3i, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 do l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf\" title=\"Antonio Conte Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Eden-Hazard-phat-bieu-ve-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chia tay Conte, Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri thay th\u1ebf</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Daily Star c\u00f2n cho bi\u1ebft th\u00eam, HLV Sarri y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf khu Cobham, Surrey, g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a CLB. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, c\u00f9ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u00eam 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa. 2 b\u00ean s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Sarri c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1eddi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea &ndash; Gianfranco Zola gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, v\u00ec The Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. Nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Hazard hay Courtois c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 t\u00e2n HLV v\u00e0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed cho bi\u1ebft s\u1edf d\u0129 Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111u\u1ed5i Diego Costa qua tin nh\u1eafn, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh b\u1ecb s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m th\u00ea th\u1ea3m (b\u00e1n cho Atletico v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 58 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-thu-mon-nguoi-brazil-172-189429.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois ra \u0111i qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-thu-thach-long-kien-nhan-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-bo-nhiem-sarri-chuong-su-moi-voi-ga-nhan-vien-ngan-hang-172-187380.html\">Chelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri: Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1eed m\u1edbi v\u1edbi g\u00e3 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\nChelsea b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri thay th\u1ebf HLV Conte trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao v\u00e0 qua \u0111\u00e2y, Stamford Bridge s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i, k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"555","checkdouble":"189498"}]}